name: hot balm cat
description: Accidentally when I used hot balm, my cat just lick it and really enjoy the sensation of the hot taste... I'm sure, there are many cats that love that sensation too... Besides, he was really liked to hide in a dark place and just show his glowing eyes... That's why, his name is Tanmuk (Tanpa Muka/No Face). The last time I saw him was in 2008... Miss him verymuch
